Package boundary

Class BaseBoundary

java.lang.Object
utils.Base
boundary.BaseBoundary
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProjectBoundary, RequestBoundary, UserBoundary
public class BaseBoundary extends Base
The BaseBoundary class extends the Base class and provides the basic input functionalities and access to all the boundary classes. It contains the centralManager object and input object.
Since:
2023-04-15
Version:
1.0
Author:
Esther Teo Gek Wat
